Undestanding Concepts of DevOps CI/CD pipeline

Service source code, codes to define logic to handle input and output
Service release, a specific version of definition tag with version number
Service artifact, a service definition built from source code
Service, a running state machine in a environment
Service configuration, a set of static values accepted by a service
Service configuration management, a tool to manage configurations for a service running in a environment
Service deployment definition, a define of put release X with configuration Y to environment Z
Service deployment, an execution of a deployment definition
Environment Configuration Management, a tool to provision an environment with given properties
Environment, a set of static values to a state machine
Service/Application/System, a state machine waiting for accept inputs 
